<ext_description linkend="Part_feature_location_arm.Usage_concept_usage_relationship">
<note> The text description for this Application Object has not been fully updated to agree with the EXPRESS.</note><p>

 A <b>Usage_concept_usage_relationship</b> is the association between a <express_ref linkend="Layered_interconnect_module_design:arm:Layered_interconnect_module_design_arm.Component_termination_passage_template_terminal"/>, a <express_ref linkend="Manufacturing_technology:arm:Manufacturing_technology_arm.Land_template_terminal"/>, a <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_usage_view:arm:Physical_unit_usage_view_arm.Part_feature"/>, a <express_ref linkend="Physical_layout_template:arm:Physical_layout_template_arm.Layout_template_definition"/>, a <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_usage_view:arm:Physical_unit_usage_view_arm.Part_usage_view"/>, a <express_ref linkend="Printed_physical_layout_template:arm:Printed_physical_layout_template_arm.Printed_part_template_terminal"/>, or a <express_ref linkend="Layered_interconnect_module_design:arm:Layered_interconnect_module_design_arm.Via_template_terminal"/>, as a source and a 
 <express_ref linkend="Layered_interconnect_module_design:arm:Layered_interconnect_module_design_arm.Component_termination_passage_template_terminal"/>, a  <express_ref linkend="Manufacturing_technology:arm:Manufacturing_technology_arm.Land_template_terminal"/>, a  <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_usage_view:arm:Physical_unit_usage_view_arm.Part_feature"/>, 
a  <express_ref linkend="Physical_layout_template:arm:Physical_layout_template_arm.Layout_template_definition"/>, a  <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_usage_view:arm:Physical_unit_usage_view_arm.Part_usage_view"/>, a  <express_ref linkend="Printed_physical_layout_template:arm:Printed_physical_layout_template_arm.Printed_part_template_terminal"/> or a  <express_ref linkend="Layered_interconnect_module_design:arm:Layered_interconnect_module_design_arm.Via_template_terminal"/> 
as a target. This relationship positions and orients the geometric model of the source into the model of the 
target using a transformation.
</p></ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_feature_location_arm.Usage_concept_usage_relationship.associated_usage_placement">
the <b>associated_usage_placement</b> specifies the <express_ref linkend="Elemental_geometric_shape:arm:Elemental_geometric_shape_arm.Axis_placement"/> of the target item in the coordinate system of the source item for the 
<b>Usage_concept_usage_relationship</b>, including any transformation required.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_feature_location_arm.Usage_concept_usage_relationship.associated_shape_definition"><p></p></ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_feature_location_arm.Usage_concept_usage_relationship.associated_usage">
the <b>associated_usage</b> specifies either a <express_ref linkend="Layered_interconnect_module_design:arm:Layered_interconnect_module_design_arm.Component_termination_passage_template_terminal"/>, a <express_ref linkend="Manufacturing_technology:arm:Manufacturing_technology_arm.Land_template_terminal"/>, a <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_usage_view:arm:Physical_unit_usage_view_arm.Part_feature"/>, a <express_ref linkend="Physical_layout_template:arm:Physical_layout_template_arm.Layout_template_definition"/>, a <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_usage_view:arm:Physical_unit_usage_view_arm.Part_usage_view"/>, a <express_ref linkend="Printed_physical_layout_template:arm:Printed_physical_layout_template_arm.Printed_part_template_terminal"/>, or a <express_ref linkend="Layered_interconnect_module_design:arm:Layered_interconnect_module_design_arm.Via_template_terminal"/> as the target item for the 
<b>Usage_concept_usage_relationship</b>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_feature_location_arm.Usage_concept_usage_relationship.associating_usage_shape"><p></p></ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_feature_location_arm.Usage_concept_usage_relationship.wr:WR1">
The <b>associated_shape_definition</b> and the <b>associating_usage_shape</b> shall both be either  <express_ref linkend="Non_feature_shape_element:arm:Non_feature_shape_element_arm.Non_feature_shape_definition"/> or shall both be  <express_ref linkend="Layered_shape:arm:Layered_shape_arm.Feature_shape_definition"/>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_feature_location_arm.Usage_concept_usage_relationship.wr:WR2">
If the <b>associated_usage_placement</b> is a Cartesian_transformation_operator_2d, the <b>associating_usage_shape</b> shall be a  <express_ref linkend="Non_feature_shape_element:arm:Non_feature_shape_element_arm.Non_feature_shape_definition"/>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_feature_location_arm.Usage_concept_usage_relationship.wr:WR3">
The associated_usage_origin shall be the origin referenced by the shape_origin attribute of <b>associated_shape_definition</b>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_feature_location_arm.Usage_concept_usage_relationship.wr:WR4">
No member specified by <b>associated_usage</b> or by associating_usage shall be an ancestor or descendant of itself.
</ext_description>
</ext_descriptions>
